data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! SELLER WILL CONSIDER CLOSING COST CONTRIBUTION! Discover the epitome of country living combined with new and updated amenities. This house is a true gem! Upon driving up to the house you will notice its stunning curb appeal. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home was built in 2020 and is sitting on nearly an acre. The kitchen will include all stainless steel appliances. And the soft close kitchen cabinets and drawers are just a bonus! If you are looking for a home that is up to date with technology look no further! It has motion censored lights in the bathrooms. Smart switches that are compatible with Alexa. A central in floor vacuum system, a wifi enabled thermostat, an interior bug/pest control system, and so much more. If the house doesn't already have you hooked the fully fenced in backyard will! The insulated screened in back porch is perfect for entertaining guest. There is access to set up a tv in the corner of the porch. So bring your grill and turn on the latest game and enjoy the nice cool air inside when you open your French doors that lead into the kitchen! Just a few feet away from your back porch is a charming pool. Great for those summer days. There is a covered carport with its own access that is perfect for an RV. The workshop in the back is insulated and lofted. Need a place to work on your toys so you're not sitting out in the hot Florida sun? The workshop has a window unit so you can stay cool all year round! It is as cute outside as it is inside! This property also has a covered concrete slab carport. This can hold up to two cars. There is an additional concrete slab that connects to it which would be perfect for an extra car, boat, or trailer. So bring all your toys, this spacious backyard has plenty of room! This home is sure to check all your boxes and more! Don't forget to check out the playhouse it is sure to impress!
